### mammals limbs

- why mmmals have four limbs?
  - dogs and cats have two forelegs and two hind legs
  - humans have legs and arms
  -why don't humans or horses have six legs?

- are four limbs an evolutionary adaptation?
  - four legged animals can run, hunt, and graze
  - humans and other apes can not only walk or run, but use hands to manipulate objects

